  <section class="category-info-block">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>DGSDK Industrial Equipment — Product Overview</h2>
      <p>DGSDK is a manufacturer based in Dongguan, China, specializing in static elimination systems, industrial cleaning machines, precision CNC machined parts, and automation equipment for electronics and display manufacturing. Our products are used across PCB production, flat panel display manufacturing, optical film processing, and industrial automation applications.</p>

      <h3>Static Elimination Systems</h3>
      <p>Our <a href="/products/static-eliminator">static elimination systems</a> remove electrostatic charge from surfaces, materials, and components during manufacturing. Static charge attracts dust and particles to product surfaces, causing defects during inspection and assembly. DGSDK manufactures ion bar static eliminators, blower-type ionizers, spot ionizers, and high-voltage power supplies for industrial use. These systems are widely used in PCB manufacturing, flat panel display production, optical film processing, and electronics assembly.</p>

      <h3>Industrial Cleaning Machines</h3>
      <p>Our <a href="/products/cleaning-machine">industrial cleaning machines</a> use adhesive roller technology to remove particles, dust, and contamination from substrate surfaces without chemicals or water. We manufacture PCB cleaning machines, SMT inline cleaners, FPC cleaning machines, optical film cleaners, polarizer cleaners, LCM module cleaners, and backlight panel cleaners. Each machine is designed for a specific substrate type and production line configuration.</p>

      <h3>Precision CNC Machined Parts</h3>
      <p>Our <a href="/products/precision-machined-parts">precision machined parts</a> are manufactured using CNC milling, CNC turning, and lathe machining processes. We supply brackets, fixing plates, shaft-end components, connection blocks, and front panels to tight dimensional tolerances. Materials include aluminum alloy, carbon steel, and stainless steel. Custom parts are produced from customer drawings for OEM and prototype applications.</p>

      <h3>Industrial Automation Equipment</h3>
      <p>Our <a href="/products/automation">automation equipment</a> includes integrated production lines for diffusion plate cleaning and inspection, robotic loading and unloading cleaning systems, and polarizer axis angle measuring instruments. Each automation system is engineered to reduce manual handling, improve process consistency, and integrate with existing production line equipment.</p>

      <p>Contact us to discuss your production requirements and receive a product recommendation or custom solution proposal.</p>
    </div>
